BT /F1 11 Tf 72 720 Td (Support means the primary test clears the threshold in section 6, the H2 placebo shows no) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 705.2 Td (comparable lead, and the result survives the search-saturation check \(the same result across) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 690.4 Td (different baseline windows\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 670.6 Td (Kill condition. If, after four quarters of data, the signal does not show a statistically significant) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 655.8 Td (positive lead-lag relationship with realized occupational unemployment in the high-exposure) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 641 Td (group at the threshold above, we treat the predictive claim as unsupported, we publish that, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 626.2 Td (we either re-scope to a descriptive-only signal or shelve it. We commit to this now, while we) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 611.4 Td (still do not know the answer.) Tj ET
